data.description: Great value in Holland! Four bedrooms and two full bathrooms, including a first floor master suite! Feels like new construction, a ton of updates! All newer flooring throughout (January 2024) remodeled kitchen with all countertops, flooring and cabinets being replaced, and stainless steel appliances.  Huge family room in the back make this home perfect for entertaining.  Both bathrooms have been completely remodeled.  Vinyl siding on the exterior, newer windows, there really is nothing to do but move in.  Hurry on this one!
